The following Ares files are derived from Codex source:

- packages/core/src/applyPatch/parser.ts
    Ported from codex-rs/apply-patch/src/parser.rs.
    Implements the `*** Begin Patch / *** Update File / @@ context`
    grammar with lenient mode for the GPT-4.1 heredoc-quoting bug.

- (planned, M4) packages/tools/src/CodeMode.ts
    Conceptual port of codex-rs/code-mode/src/{description,runtime}.rs.
    The `exec` tool that lets the model write JS calling other tools
    as `await tools.foo(...)`, with the `// @exec: {...}` pragma and
    helpers (text, image, store, load, notify, yield_control).

